<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Problem Statement</p>

    <ul>
      <li>A variable x is provided to you.</li>
      <li>Repeatedly decrease the value of the variable <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">x</code> by 3 each time, as long as <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">x</code> is greater than or equal to 0.</li>
      <li>Print the number of times the iteration runs.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
</ul>

